{% extends "base.html.j2" %}

{% block title %}
{% if language == 'tr' %}Talebiniz Reddedildi - {{ location_name }}{% elif language == 'en' %}Your Claim Has Been Rejected - {{ location_name }}{% else %}Uw Claim is Afgewezen - {{ location_name }}{% endif %}
{% endblock %}

{% block header_subtitle %}
<p>
    {% if language == 'tr' %}
        Konum talebiniz reddedildi
    {% elif language == 'en' %}
        Your location claim has been rejected
    {% else %}
        Uw locatie claim is afgewezen
    {% endif %}
</p>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
{% if language == 'tr' %}
<p>Merhaba {{ user_name }},</p>

<p>Maalesef, <strong>{{ location_name }}</strong> için yaptığınız claim talebi reddedildi.</p>

{% if rejection_reason %}
<p><strong>Red nedeni:</strong> {{ rejection_reason }}</p>
{% endif %}

<p>Eğer bu karar hakkında sorularınız varsa veya yeni bilgiler paylaşmak isterseniz, lütfen bizimle iletişime geçmekten çekinmeyin.</p>

<p>Başka bir konum için claim talebinde bulunabilirsiniz.</p>

<p>Teşekkürler,<br>Turkspot Ekibi</p>

{% elif language == 'en' %}
<p>Hello {{ user_name }},</p>

<p>Unfortunately, your claim request for <strong>{{ location_name }}</strong> has been rejected.</p>

{% if rejection_reason %}
<p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{ rejection_reason }}</p>
{% endif %}

<p>If you have questions about this decision or would like to share additional information, please don't hesitate to reach out to us.</p>

<p>You can submit a claim request for another location.</p>

<p>Thank you,<br>The Turkspot Team</p>

{% else %}
<p>Hoi {{ user_name }},</p>

<p>Helaas is uw claim verzoek voor <strong>{{ location_name }}</strong> afgewezen.</p>

{% if rejection_reason %}
<p><strong>Reden:</strong> {{ rejection_reason }}</p>
{% endif %}

<p>Als u vragen heeft over deze beslissing of aanvullende informatie wilt delen, aarzel dan niet om contact met ons op te nemen.</p>

<p>U kunt een claim verzoek indienen voor een andere locatie.</p>

<p>Bedankt,<br>Het Turkspot Team</p>
{% endif %}
{% endblock %}

